Package koopa.core.grammars

Class KoopaGrammar

java.lang.Object
koopa.core.grammars.Grammar
koopa.core.grammars.KoopaGrammar
Direct Known Subclasses:
CICSBaseGrammar, CobolPreprocessingBaseGrammar, DirectivesBaseGrammar, SQLBaseGrammar
public abstract class KoopaGrammar extends Grammar
This provides the basis for implementing full grammars. It basically gives you a form of parser combinators with which you can define more complex grammar rules.

Note that you shouldn't be using this class directly. Instead the actual code will get generated from Koopa grammar definitions.
